{"tid":726712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希床上親熱短片曝光  秦舒培露粉紅底洩春光","createTime":"2018-07-02T15:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T10:47:34.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c16dc9cff62131de426e0f92cc2b3bc61f0e6b9","tid":726712,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"陳冠希（Edison）同大陸名模秦舒培打得火熱，最近兩人為服裝品牌Entireworld拍攝短片，公然在床上晒恩愛甜到漏，兩人頭貼頭瞓喺床上，Edison又錫又搓秦舒培隻手仔，着熱褲嘅秦舒培春心蕩漾，用長腿撩撥挑逗Edison，之後更一個轉身攬着他，然而，長腿在轉動間動作太大，露出粉紅色底褲同半截pat pat，不慎洩春光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛起哄，留言：「秀恩愛的時候可以忘掉Alaia」、「冠希看舒培那一下的笑容甜死了」，有眼利嘅網民更估拍攝地點似係兩人愛巢，事關Edison曾在ig晒秦舒培同囡囡Alaia熟睡相，比對床同枕頭都係一模一樣。36歲嘅Edison同細10歲嘅秦舒培拍拖兩年，現育有1歲女兒Alaia，做咗爸爸嘅Edison修心養性，去年8月豪擲2千300萬港元在洛杉磯買愛巢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180702/58390971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58390971&d=wYJ3saCtSGZJu1oBX3652fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4ab7c4f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58390971&h=f4103b67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180702/58390971</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/233343_ec6b950652cffaa31d753eaaedd790e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F233343_ec6b950652cffaa31d753eaaedd790e2.jpg&h=e338036b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/233343_b1f7575bb0d08bc47f88aeb7b5b920c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F233343_b1f7575bb0d08bc47f88aeb7b5b920c4.jpg&h=6a2b3941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1336481c08ee972f54d66bf7a4708db2b343996","tid":726712,"uid":61005,"like":0,